OL,3,CPolice officer injured as public urged
OL,4,Cto avoid Tamworth hotel area
OL,6,FA police officer has been injured in
OL,7,Fviolence at a Holiday Inn hotel in
OL,8,FTamworth tonight (4th August).
OL,10,FOfficers are urging the public to
OL,11,Favoid the area around the hotel in the
OL,12,Ftown in Staffordshire.
OL,14,FSpecialist officers are continuing to
OL,15,Fdeal with what officers describe as
OL,16,F"violent acts of thuggery".
