OL,6,FHundreds of people gathered in
OL,7,FNottingham yesterday, from so-called
OL,8,Ffar-right and anti-racist groups.
OL,10,FPolice had to form a human line to
OL,11,Fseparate the rival protestors in Old
OL,12,FMarket Square.
OL,14,FIn Stoke-on-Trent ten people have been
OL,15,Farrested after protests turned violent.
