OL,6,FThe protests and counter-protests in
OL,7,FHanley involved hundreds of people,
OL,8,Fand were followed by outbreaks of
OL,9,Fviolence with missiles thrown in
OL,10,Fclashes on Saturday (August 3rd)
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,13,FIn a similar incident to Tamworth
OL,14,Ftoday (4th August), a Holiday Inn
OL,15,Fhousing asylum seekers was attacked in
OL,16,FRotherham.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,19,Fpromised that those involved in unrest
OL,20,Fwill "face the full force of the law".
